 :tx/rationale "Create task: EPIC: Concept Crystallization Engine — OBSERVER-6 implementation via Piagetian developmental epistemology. CONTEXT: DOGFOOD-2 Session 2 scored 3.3/10, BELOW Session 1 baseline (4.0). Root cause: keyword Jaccard (100 bits) discards LLM's semantic structure (100K bits). Every DOGFOOD dimension depends on connection quality, which depends on preserving semantic similarity. THE ARCHITECTURE: Five layers that compose into a cognitive partner for LLM agents. LAYER 1 (EMBED): Semantic embeddings via model2vec/potion-128M — 256-dim dense vectors computed locally, offline, <1ms, deterministic. Stored as :exploration/embedding Bytes datoms. Replaces Jaccard as primary connection signal. LAYER 2 (CONCEPT): Concept entities that emerge from embedding clusters. Schema: :concept/name, :concept/description, :concept/embedding (centroid), :concept/member-count, :concept/created-at. Observations link via :exploration/concept Ref. Concepts split when variance exceeds threshold, merge when centroids converge. This IS OBSERVER-6 (Ontology Discovery). LAYER 3 (INNATE): Five universal schemas seeded at braid init — components, dependencies, invariants, patterns, anomalies. These are the Piagetian sensorimotor reflexes: initial scaffolding for concept formation. From the policy manifest (C8 compliant — different domains can have different innate schemas). LAYER 4 (LINK): Entity auto-linking at observe time. Scan text for known entity names (package names from bootstrap, spec IDs, concept names). Auto-create Ref datoms. Combined with embeddings: entity links provide STRUCTURAL connections, embeddings provide SEMANTIC connections. LAYER 5 (STEER): Concept-aware responses from braid status and braid observe. Every CLI response is a steering vector in the LLM's latent space. observe returns concept membership + structural gap + steering question. status returns innate schema progress + concept inventory + coverage map + frontier. DEVELOPMENTAL TRAJECTORY: sensorimotor (innate schemas + raw observations) → concrete operational (domain-specific concepts emerge) → formal operational (cross-cutting abstractions). MEMETIC TRANSMISSION: concepts transfer across projects via CRDT merge. Cultural selection of useful schemas. Braid's 42 sessions of self-knowledge become the genome for offspring sessions. VERIFICATION: DOGFOOD-3 on Go CLI with same protocol. Target: overall 7+/10 (was 3.3). Connection quality 7+ (was 3.0). Discovery 6+ (was 2.3). TRACES: ADR-FOUNDATION-015 (Observer Formalism), ADR-FOUNDATION-016 (Observation-Projection Duality), ADR-FOUNDATION-014 (Convergence Thesis), SEED.md S7 (Self-Improvement). SUPERSEDES: CE-STEER (t-e7394fd8), partially supersedes CE-TEMP (t-8e8cf412), CE-TOPO (t-5db2efb0)."
